05Dt 17:19 It shall remain with him the rest of his life so he may learn to fear the Lord his God and observe all the words of this Law and these statutes, in order to fulfill them. 
05Dt 17:20 He is not to exalt himself over his relatives, nor turn aside from the commandment - neither to the right nor to the left - so that he and his sons may reign long in Israel."
05Dt 18:1 "The Levitical priests, the whole tribe of Levi, will not have a portion or an inheritance within Israel. Instead, they will eat the burnt offerings of the Lord, because that is their inheritance. 
