05Dt 18:11 casts spells, or who is a medium, an occultist, or a necromancer. 
05Dt 18:12 Whoever practices these things is detestable to the Lord, and the Lord your God will expel them before you because of these things. 
05Dt 18:13 You must be completely faithful to the Lord your God, 
