05Dt 20:12 But if they refuse to make peace with you and instead choose war, then attack it. 
05Dt 20:13 The Lord your God will deliver it into your control, and you must execute every male. 
05Dt 20:14 The women, children, all the livestock in the city, and all of the spoil and plunder will belong to you. Appropriate the spoil of your enemies, which the Lord your God will give you. 
