05Dt 20:18 so they won't teach you to do all the detestable things that they do for their gods. If you do what they teach you, you will sin against the Lord your God."
05Dt 20:19 "When you attack a city and have to fight against it for many days, don't destroy its trees by cutting them down with an ax. You may eat from them, but you must not cut them down. Are the trees of the field human beings, that you would come and attack them?
