05Dt 21:10 "If you go to battle against your enemies, and the Lord your God delivers them into your control, you may take some prisoners captive. 
05Dt 21:11 If you see among the prisoners a beautiful woman and you desire her, then you may take her as your wife. 
05Dt 21:12 Bring her to your house, but shave her head and trim her nails. 
05Dt 21:13 Remove her prisoner's clothing and let her remain for a month in your house, mourning her parents. After that, you may become her husband and she shall become your wife. 
05Dt 21:14 If you aren't pleased with her and you send her away, you must not sell her for money or mistreat her, since you have dishonored her."2111
