08Ru 2:3 So she went out, proceeded to the field, and gleaned behind the harvesters. And it happened that she came to the portion of land belonging to Boaz, of the family of Elimelech.
08Ru 2:4 Now when Boaz arrived from Bethlehem, he said to the harvesters, "The Lord be with you." "May the Lord bless you!" they replied.
08Ru 2:5 At this point, Boaz asked the foreman of his harvesters, "To whom does this young woman belong?"
